{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/how-to-use-aws-ec2-free-tier","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"168bf988-f079-5a56-8890-7b718fb4f04c","html":"<p>클라우드 서버를 알아보다가 AWS(Amazon Web Service)에서 제공하는 EC2를 사용해보기로 했다.</p>\n<p>이 서비스는 1년 동안 무료로 이용 가능한 프리티어(Free Tier)를 제공한다. </p>\n<h3 id=\"프리티어-시작하기계정-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B0%EC%96%B4-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0%EA%B3%84%EC%A0%95-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"프리티어 시작하기계정 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프리티어 시작하기(계정 생성)</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/e67a8/ec2_free_tier_web_site.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/8ac56/ec2_free_tier_web_site.webp 240w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/d3be9/ec2_free_tier_web_site.webp 480w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/e46b2/ec2_free_tier_web_site.webp 960w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/f992d/ec2_free_tier_web_site.webp 1440w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/31418/ec2_free_tier_web_site.webp 1740w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/8ff5a/ec2_free_tier_web_site.png 240w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/e85cb/ec2_free_tier_web_site.png 480w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/d9199/ec2_free_tier_web_site.png 960w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/07a9c/ec2_free_tier_web_site.png 1440w,\n/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/e67a8/ec2_free_tier_web_site.png 1740w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ee809cd19403ded33e5938a31173ceb1/d9199/ec2_free_tier_web_site.png\"\n            alt=\"ec2_free_tier_web_site.png\"\n            title=\"ec2_free_tier_web_site.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span> <em><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/ko/free/?all-free-tier.sort-by=item.additionalFields.SortRank&#x26;all-free-tier.sort-order=asc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">AWS 프리티어 웹사이트</a></em></p>\n<p>계정 생성 후 해외 결제가 가능한 카드를 등록 해야한다. 이때 등록 후 1달러가 결제된다. 실제 있는 카드인지 확인을 위해서 등록한다. 그 후 빠른시일내에 다시 환불된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"리전-선택\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%A0%84-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D\" aria-label=\"리전 선택 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>리전 선택</h3>\n<p>로그인 후 <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/ko/ec2/?nc2=type_a&#x26;ec2-whats-new.sort-by=item.additionalFields.postDateTime&#x26;ec2-whats-new.sort-order=desc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">EC2 사이트로</a> 접속해서 제일 먼저 리전을 서울로 변경한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 734px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/c6d67/region_list.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 118.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/8ac56/region_list.webp 240w,\n/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/d3be9/region_list.webp 480w,\n/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/a242a/region_list.webp 734w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 734px) 100vw, 734px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/8ff5a/region_list.png 240w,\n/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/e85cb/region_list.png 480w,\n/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/c6d67/region_list.png 734w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 734px) 100vw, 734px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/3675e29a26f442fd40e6ffb6b8b47070/c6d67/region_list.png\"\n            alt=\"region_list.png\"\n            title=\"region_list.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span> <em>리전 리스트</em></p>\n<p>그리고 화면 중간에 인스턴스 시작을 눌러 인스턴스를 생성한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"인스턴스-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B4%EC%8A%A4-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"인스턴스 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인스턴스 생성</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/f238d/instance_start.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.416666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/8ac56/instance_start.webp 240w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/d3be9/instance_start.webp 480w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/e46b2/instance_start.webp 960w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/f992d/instance_start.webp 1440w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/882b9/instance_start.webp 1920w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/cc0a6/instance_start.webp 2078w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/8ff5a/instance_start.png 240w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/e85cb/instance_start.png 480w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/d9199/instance_start.png 960w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/07a9c/instance_start.png 1440w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/29114/instance_start.png 1920w,\n/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/f238d/instance_start.png 2078w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d72c5ea2d2f55ea7af12b6e1c07f49b1/d9199/instance_start.png\"\n            alt=\"instance_start.png\"\n            title=\"instance_start.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span> <em>인스턴스 시작</em></p>\n<p>제일 처음 사용할 OS를 선택한다. 리스트 중 <strong>프리티어 사용 가능</strong>인 OS를 선택해서 인스턴스를 생성하면 된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"os-리스트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#os-%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"os 리스트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>OS 리스트</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/776d3/os_list.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.16666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/8ac56/os_list.webp 240w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/d3be9/os_list.webp 480w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/e46b2/os_list.webp 960w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/f992d/os_list.webp 1440w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/dcb16/os_list.webp 1814w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/8ff5a/os_list.png 240w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/e85cb/os_list.png 480w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/d9199/os_list.png 960w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/07a9c/os_list.png 1440w,\n/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/776d3/os_list.png 1814w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/fd2936c0e7301fe8024f3231dbe92715/d9199/os_list.png\"\n            alt=\"os_list.png\"\n            title=\"os_list.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span> <em>OS list</em></p>\n<p>필자는 Amazon Linux 2 AMI를 이용해서 생성하기로 했다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"인스턴스-선택\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B4%EC%8A%A4-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D\" aria-label=\"인스턴스 선택 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인스턴스 선택</h3>\n<p>OS를 선택하면 인스턴스 리스트가 뜬다. 이때 프리티어 전용 인스턴스(t2.micro)가 있다. 이걸 선택하고 하단에 바로 <strong>검토 및 시작</strong>으로 넘어가면 된다. 만약 본인이 추가적인 설정을 하고 싶다면 <strong>다음</strong>버튼을 클릭하여 다음 단계로 넘어가면 된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/776d3/instance_list.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/8ac56/instance_list.webp 240w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/d3be9/instance_list.webp 480w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/e46b2/instance_list.webp 960w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/f992d/instance_list.webp 1440w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/dcb16/instance_list.webp 1814w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/8ff5a/instance_list.png 240w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/e85cb/instance_list.png 480w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/d9199/instance_list.png 960w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/07a9c/instance_list.png 1440w,\n/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/776d3/instance_list.png 1814w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/452ee9ea5c0a7e53cba59791c6bb3da5/d9199/instance_list.png\"\n            alt=\"instance_list.png)\"\n            title=\"instance_list.png)\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span> <em>인스턴스 리스트</em></p>\n<p><strong>추가</strong> 웹서버 오픈시 80, 8080포트를 열어야한다면 8단계 보안그룹에서 수정하거나 따로 수정 가능하다. 설명은 제일 하단에서 설명하겠다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"검토-및-시작\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%80%ED%86%A0-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91\" aria-label=\"검토 및 시작 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>검토 및 시작</h3>\n<p>해당 단계에서는 본인이 선택한 사항과 기본적으로 선택된 사항들을 보여주고 키페어 파일을 생성한다. 키페어 파일을 이용해 SSH 접속이 가능하다. 해당 파일은 재발급이 불가능하기 때문에 반드시 저장해야하며 분실하지 말아야한다.</p>\n<p>생성 완료 후 상단의 서비스 > EC2 > 인스턴스로 들어가면 생성된 인스턴스를 확인 할 수 있으며</p>\n<p>해당 화면에서 인스턴스를 on / off / reload / delete가 가능하다.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/how-to-use-aws-ec2-free-tier","tagSlugs":["/tag/aws/","/tag/aws-ec-2/","/tag/free-tier/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-10-11T11:16:07.000Z","description":"AWS EC2 프리티어를 이용해서 서버를 오픈해보자!","tags":["AWS","AWS EC2","Free Tier"],"title":"AWS EC2 프리티어를 이용해보자","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/7bc74752bcabdad1be6f7ca8fca76917/ec2_free_tier.png"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/how-to-use-aws-ec2-free-tier"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1118307107","251939775","401334301"]}